    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247710/extras/b33431405b12e6f6bcc199dd508117ea.avif?t=1753969387\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3247710/extras_big/b33431405b12e6f6bcc199dd508117ea.avif?t=1753969387 width=800 height=188 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The second game of Mad Miner, a dystopia where humans are forced to live in mines, takes place in the third dimension! Our main character joins the research team as a miner on a mission to dig deeper with his pickaxe.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mad Miner 2 shares the same character and universe as the first game, but with a completely different story. With 3D stylized graphics, you will feel like you are really there as you walk through the narrow and long corridors of the mines.</p>",
